➜广东诗人小隐：长相思．美如卿
http://www.sohu.com/a/429991483_100115135	36586
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201106/b8df382d4a6448558536fc5c7fe588ee.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>长相思．美如卿</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/小隐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爱有情，恨有情。情到浓时万事轻。今生不愿醒。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">日还倾，夜还倾。醉里江山青外青。画中如美卿。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201106/4afbb69706a14559b3d6068d31f1afe2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>小隐，自由职业者，一个游走人间的过客，喜欢用文字与灵魂对话的小女人，左手柴米油盐酱拌醋～右手诗词歌赋花间茶～</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201106/38555126e47a425384e8a5b2d1417f58.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
