➜罗红建：《一棵树的思想》
http://www.sohu.com/a/429993330_100115135	37022
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201106/38af90d7fc994b33bff68852bdad60e5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《一棵树的思想》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/罗红建</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">半尺霜白，皆被敛于发际</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">连着曲卷的心思，昨夜都给了叶子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">却羞得个个腮红耳赤，掩面而逃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">她们全然不知，那天的桃花也是如此</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>蛰伏的名字，被一只夜莺叫醒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>继而，躁动于远处霓虹之下</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>可月色竟是如此的白，苍白如水……</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>几枚懒散的星子斜挂</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>应是，那年你我数过的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>就留给夜吧！由它苟且</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>正如场场大雪，亦容我败兵偷生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无处安放的依然无处安放</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">飘零，并不全是风雨之后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">痕迹和溶解，也总是相互背弃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最终，都归了尘土</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>落吧！落尽！落尽成谶</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
