➜河南诗人田书芹：五言律诗押平韵（十六首）
http://www.sohu.com/a/429995462_100115135	37793
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201106/030c3b16be2542bf9c58c9aeb27b3b14.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五言律诗押平韵（十六首）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>观海（一）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">独立高岩上，临风远望台。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">茫茫天水接，滚滚浪涛来。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">潮落鸥鸣戏，云低舰照开。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人生常起伏，有志展奇才。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2016.7.5</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>观海（二）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">独站矶头顶，浩然奔我来。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">茫茫天水接，冉冉紫霞裁。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">逐浪银鸥舞，巡洋铁舰开。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">欣然思起伏，敢博上高台。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2019.7.11</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>梦</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">午睡逢潇雨，清凉入幻相。</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">门前桐影壮，院内桂花香。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">狗戏球儿转，猫追蝶舞忙。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天雷惊梦破，沉醉旧时光。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2019.7.12</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>书法</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">书法蕴人道，时时苦练千。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">笔锋呈剑气，横撇秀山川。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">磨出谦卑态，修来礼义篇。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">纸笺方寸地，淡墨赞先贤。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2019.7.24</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201106/b1b8775851de46e2990d94f659ad82aa.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>贺蓝星二院启航</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">公益全程教，倾身育德章。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">孜孜传国粹，矻矻为群芳。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">学子挥毫洒，评诗对仗忙。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">众人幽趣至，叫我喜心房。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2020.2.25</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>滨海之畔</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹 </strong> </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">苍茫滨海地，旖旎广无边。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">水榭摇红影，危楼接碧天。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">花香蜂蝶吻，日丽雀莺旋。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">祥瑞和平景，挥毫抒美篇。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2019.7.14</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>滨海畔</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">苍茫滨海畔，静坐听涛声。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">归雁蓝天舞，新莺绿树争。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">花繁呈锦绣，叶密赖春生。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">兴旺清明地，昌隆气势宏。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2019.7.18</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>独处</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹 </strong> </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">闲坐旭阳迎，依林听鸟声。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">芊芊松色染，滴滴石泉清。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">竹径通幽菊，箫音对锦筝。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">欣然心寂静，畅意话诗情。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2019.7.29</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201106/12519ba7d9ec434c861b43d37cbac294.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>咏蒲公英</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">生长靠苍天，风吹色更妍。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">黄花招蛱蝶，白伞越山川。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">清热无肝火，消痰有利咽。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">全身皆是宝，入药美名传。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2019.7.30</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>竹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">品乃真君子，容妆着翠衣。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">风吹腾碧浪，叶舞现青辉。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不羡桃梨艳，敢超松柏威。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">标高虚劲节，浩气入云飞。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2020.8.23</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>感怀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">日照山川亮，闲观地洞仙。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">珍禽林里走，幽鹿穴中眠。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">涧水清波舞，鹂声绿树穿。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自然生态好，谐美太平天。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2020.8.24</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>偶遇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乡村闲信步，向晚意千千。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">远处归林鸟，谁家起灶烟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">闻童吹短笛，遇士赋诗篇。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相问浮生事？皆言付管弦。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2020.8.29</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201106/7b85ac26c41b4085b54db9eda20d2bb1.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>顿觉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一路满山芳，千峰草木香。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">行闻黄鸟弄，坐见白云乡。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">顿觉生如梦，俄惊鬓似霜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今应思秉烛，游个夜无央。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2020.9.10</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>咏荷</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">婷婷玉立丛，菡萏魅无穷。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">水里藏依旧，人前秀不同。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">争奇烟锁翠，斗艳蕊摇红。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">出污身不染，标高自洁风。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2020.9.11</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>怀远</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长提幕晚风，弯月影朦胧。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">溪水孤村绕。竹林一径通。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">三杯君莫笑，万语酒相融。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">怀远思兄弟，吹笙念不穷。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2020.9.18</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>深山寺院</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">深山寺院藏，古树绕经房。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">汩汩溪流水，微微野菊香。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">芝兰知旧雨，松柏晓新霜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">心处闲云外，参禅拜佛堂。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2019.7.19</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201106/a6acfa1eb49a43f39b101f5990089247.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】</strong>田书芹，河南内乡县人，喜欢体育，特长篮球，中国诗歌网会员，有多篇文章和诗词在内乡亲民网发表。诗写祖国大好河山，词写自己梦想人生！现为《星连文学社》编委。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201106/944bee2650fc4ba0a6758436f0f5379c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
